amendatorysection.para: Sections 38-1201 to 38-1239 shall be known and may be cited as the Emergency Medical Services Practice Act.

source.note: The Revisor of Statutes has pursuant to section 49-769 correlated LB910, section 1, with LB1355, section 1, to reflect all amendments.
Changes made by LB910 became operative July 1, 2025. Changes made by LB1355 became operative April 17, 2024.
